      "title": "Geekatplay Overlay Showcase",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "1. Load a base clip in the left GAP video loader.\n2. Load a second clip in the right GAP video loader to use as the overlay layer.\n3. Use GAPLayerComposer to place the overlay as picture-in-picture, blend it, and duck the base audio while it is visible.\n4. Add a title or lower third with GAPMotionTextFX after the layer composite.\n5. Export the final result with GAPVideoExporter.\n6. No extra checkpoints, VAEs, or text encoders are required for this workflow. Put source videos in ComfyUI/input or upload them directly in GAPLoadVideoUI."
      ],
      "color": "#223",
      "bgcolor": "#335"
    },
